Comments about MDI

This sample demonstrates the MultiDocument Interface standard.
It implements splitter bars, child windows (documents), and
other features; and paints the windows appropriately.

File list:

app.c		MDI sample application source file
app.def		Definition file
app.h		Resource IDs
app.ico		Icon
app.lnk		LINK helper file
app.rc 		Application resource file
appdata.c	Contains application global variables
appdata.h 	Exports application variables
appdoc.c 	Application window procedures and main routines
appinit.c	MDI initialization functions
arrange.c 	Window arrangement code
arrange.h 	The public interface to arrange.c
hsplit.ptr 	Horizontal split pointer
hvsplit.ptr 	Horizontal/vertical split pointer
mdi 		Makefile
mdi.c 		MDI application
mdi.h 		Resource IDs
mdi.ico		MDI application icon
mdi.rc 		Resource file
mdidata.c 	More global variables
mdidata.h 	More global exports
mdidoc.c 	Window routines
mdiinit.c 	Initialization code
mdisplit.c 	Splitter bar implementation
readme		You saw it here first!
vsplit.ptr	Vertical split pointer
